STATE v. DUNSTON. No. COA05-391. North Carolina Court of Appeals. Filed January 17, 2006. Certification Date February 6, 2006. Appeal from Wale (03CRS76832, 03CRS76833, 03CRS76834).

Case reported without published opinion. No error in part; Vacate the conspiracy to deliver cocaine conviction and remand.
